message.entry: Incorrect number of input arguments. Parameter names and values must occur in pairs.
First argument must be a real numeric or logical array.
Interval bound arguments must be real and numeric.
Lower bound argument must be less than or equal to the upper bound argument.
''InputMin'' value must be real and numeric.
''InputMax'' value must be real and numeric.
Lower bound of the input range must be less than or equal to the upper bound of the input range.
Dimensions of interval bound arguments must equal the dimensions of the first argument or equal 1.
Dimensions of ''InputMin'' value must equal the dimensions of the first argument or equal 1.
Dimensions of ''InputMax'' value must equal the dimensions of the first argument or equal 1.
